title: Steel-Eating Player
description: Steel-Eating Player Manhwa Lee Hyunwook, the steel emperor, was the last savior of mankind, but died. In order to change the future, the place he regressed to was… The military?!! “Why here of all places?!” The start of Corporal Lee Hyunwook, who gets stronger in a special way, by doing a steel mukbang!
